      "comment": "SUPREME COMMAND (3) has switched yards since finishing fourth two weeks ago over 1300m at this track. Proven heavy track contender with the key jockey change. Go close. PRANCING WITH FIRE (6) excellent return when second first-up, then ran below expectations over 1300m here with an ordinary ninth. Fitter now and has a sound record over this trip. Improver. BABY RYAN (2) back sharply in class when he ploughed through the heavy conditions to salute over 1300m at this track. Leading player capable of winning again. RESURRECTED (1) three weeks between runs when he faded late to run sixth over 1605m at Ballina. Suitably placed today with the senior rider going on from the good gate.",
